
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Valentine's Invitation</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background: #fff0f6;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			height: 100vh;
			margin: 0;
			font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
		}
		.card {
			background: #fff;
			border-radius: 24px;
			box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(214, 38, 61, 0.15);
			padding: 48px 32px;
			text-align: center;
			max-width: 350px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
		.heart {
			font-size: 3rem;
			color: #e63946;
			margin-bottom: 16px;
			animation: heart-beat 1s infinite cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1);
			display: inline-block;
		}
		@keyframes heart-beat {
			0% { transform: scale(1); }
			10% { transform: scale(1.2); }
			20% { transform: scale(1.1); }
			30% { transform: scale(1.25); }
			40% { transform: scale(1.1); }
			50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
			60% { transform: scale(1.05); }
			100% { transform: scale(1); }
		}
		.title {
			font-size: 2rem;
			color: #d7263d;
			margin-bottom: 16px;
			font-weight: bold;
		}
		.message {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			color: #333;
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}
		.invite-link {
			display: inline-block;
			padding: 12px 28px;
			background: #e63946;
			color: #fff;
			border-radius: 24px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			font-weight: bold;
			transition: background 0.2s;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #fff0f6;
		}
		.invite-link:hover {
			background: #d7263d;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="card">
		<div class="heart">❤️</div>
		<div class="title">Mi gran y único amor</div>
		<div class="message">Por favor oprime este botón</div>
		<a class="invite-link" href="https://192.168.1.5:8080/render/valentines">Accept Invitation</a>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
